# ACCS App Builder Drop-in

## Context

This project is a **custom drop-in** for Adobe Commerce as a Cloud Service (ACCS) App Builder extension.

## Requirements

- Target: Adobe Commerce as a Cloud Service (SaaS)
- License: Adobe Commerce Drop-in License Agreement (ACCS and Adobe Commerce Optimizer only for v3.x)
- Use official tech stack, best practices, and design patterns from Adobe components

## Compatibility

- Adobe Commerce 2.4.7+ (Storefront Compatibility Package 4.7.x)
- @dropins/tools@~1.7.0
- Node 22 (per .nvmrc)

## Best Practices

- Follow B2C/B2B drop-in patterns for consistency
- Use SDK components and design tokens
- Integrate with event bus for cross-drop-in communication
- Support Universal Editor and Document Authoring when applicable
